        "sha": "2b83bc106226993e4520c1bcb066ef8e31476326",
        "author": "Jake Marsh",
        "email": "jake@thejakemarsh.com",
        "date": "2025-12-31T18:26:01Z",
        "message": "Modernize CostumeKit with Swift Package Manager and SwiftUI support\n\n- Add Swift Package Manager support (Package.swift)\n- Modernize Swift syntax (hex.characters.count → hex.count, etc.)\n- Add full SwiftUI integration:\n  - Color.swiftUIColor extension for ColorConvertible\n  - Font.swiftUIFont extension for FontConvertible\n  - Environment integration with .costume() modifier\n  - SwiftUI Color(hex:) initializers\n- Implement darkened/lightened color methods\n- Add comprehensive test suite (17 tests)\n- Update README with full API documentation\n- Support iOS 15+, macOS 12+, tvOS 15+, watchOS 8+",
        "url": "https://github.com/jakemarsh/CostumeKit/commit/2b83bc106226993e4520c1bcb066ef8e31476326"
